#~ "Unmount all shares at once. Depending on your <link linkend="
#~ "\"configuration_page_mounting_basic_settings_behavior\">settings</link>, "
#~ "&smb4k; attempts to unmount either only those shares that are owned by "
#~ "you or all that are listed."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Desmunta totes les comparticions alhora. Depenent de les <link linkend="
#~ "\"configuration_page_mounting_basic_settings_behavior\">opcions de "
#~ "configuració</link>, el &smb4k; només intentarà desmuntar les "
#~ "comparticions que us pertanyin o totes les que es mostren."

